</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="bilibil-网页参数">Bilibil 网页参数</h2>

<table>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>key</th>
      <th>说明</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td>aid</td>
      <td>视频ID 就是B站的avxxxx 后面的数字</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>cid</td>
      <td>应该是客户端id,经测试, 这个字段不填也没关系</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>page</td>
      <td>第几个视频, 起始下标为 1 (默认值也是为1)</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>as_wide</td>
      <td>是否宽屏 1: 宽屏, 0: 小屏</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>high_quality</td>
      <td>high_quality=1 最高1080p: <br />high_quality=0 最低360p</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>danmaku</td>
      <td>是否开启弹幕 1:开启(默认), 0:关闭</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<h2 id="效果">效果</h2>

<div><div class="extensions extensions--video">
  <iframe src="//player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid=96854770&amp;page=&amp;high_quality=1&amp;danmaku=0" frameborder="no" scrolling="no" allowfullscreen="true">
  </iframe>
</div>
</div>

